file.name: openapi_validator_off.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Openapi validator off
  description: test 2 or more uri parameters
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost/api/v1
paths:
  /{param1}/{param2}:
    get:
      operationId: test2Params
      parameters:
        - name: param1
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            description: param1
        - name: param2
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            description: param2
      responses:
        '200':
          description: test
